eory if the foreign company earned $1 billion over 30 years ending in 2016,=
 and you bought 10% of the stock at the end of 2016, you owe taxes on 10% o=
f that $1 billion even if the company has made no money and the stock has *=
dropped* since then.</p>
</div>
